snippet.title: A Gummy's Life | Official Trailer | Out now on all major platforms!
snippet.description:
A Gummy's Life is out now on Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Nintendo Switch and Steam, cross-play included!

Jump into the hilarious local & online multiplayer battles:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/585190/A_Gummys_Life/?utm_source=YouTube
Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/a-gummys-life-switch/
Xbox: https://www.xbox.com/en-us/games/store/A-Gummys-Life/9NPDKHQX3QPH
PlayStation NA: https://store.playstation.com/product/UP1276-PPSA04346_00-00000000AGLPS5NA
PlayStation EU: https://store.playstation.com/es-es/product/EP1270-PPSA04347_00-00000000AGLPS5EU

Join the community on Discord: https://discord.gg/agl
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/EPGames
Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/agummyslife/

#AGummysLife #PlayStation #Xbox #NintendoSwitch #Steam
